### 6. **Complete Phaser Usage Example Pattern**

Based on HW3 assignment requirements:

```java
import static edu.rice.hj.Module0.*;
import static edu.rice.hj.Module1.*;
import edu.rice.hj.api.HjPhaser;
import edu.rice.hj.api.HjPhaserMode;
import edu.rice.hj.api.SuspendableException;

public class Example implements HjSuspendable {
    public void example() throws SuspendableException {
        // Create multiple phasers for synchronization
        HjPhaser[] phasers = new HjPhaser[numTasks];
        for (int i = 0; i < numTasks; i++) {
            phasers[i] = newPhaser(HjPhaserMode.SIG_WAIT);
        }

        // Create phased tasks
        for (int i = 0; i < numTasks; i++) {
            final int taskId = i;
            async phased(phasers[taskId], HjPhaserMode.SIG_WAIT) -> {
                for (int phase = 0; phase < numPhases; phase++) {
                    // Do work for this phase
                    doWork(1);

                    // Synchronize with other tasks at barrier
                    next();
                }
            };
        }
    }
}
```

